Summary: I took this photo out my front door. Today I noticed the object flying over the mountain.
divs: Sighting DetailsI went out my front door and noticed a beautiful clear sky and the mountain looked beautiful with the snow on it. I took a picture of it to send to my son in FL who has never seen such a sight. When I looked at the photo yesterday I noticed something obviously flying in the air just to the left of the mountain peak. I have no idea what it is and didn't notice it when I took the picture. I was hoping you could tell me what it is.
